# Firefox Extension — Popup

The popup directory is intentionally omitted: Firefox uses the same popup HTML/CSS/JS
as the Chrome extension (platform/chrome-extension/popup/). The only difference is the
background script API (browser.* vs chrome.*).

During build, copy:
  platform/chrome-extension/popup/  →  platform/firefox-extension/popup/

Or symlink:
  mklink /J platform\firefox-extension\popup platform\chrome-extension\popup
